{"tid":1950514,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好想移民？唔想一輩子困死係咁細的香港","createTime":"2020-03-30T11:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T11:48:13.000Z","uid":353419,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aa6c7d0bac8c15886bed6c904eb4180ca940d619","tid":1950514,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:19:51.000Z","msg":"一個咁細的地方要住成世，其實都幾恐怖。係同樣地方，一直重覆同樣的生活，直到老死。<br />\n<br />\n自從去左外國工作後，這種感覺更強烈，其實個世界唔係得香港，仲有其他美好的地方。<br />\n<br />\n同外國人做下朋友，係更適合的環境發展個人夢想，體會下新生活，人生才會充實。<br />\n<br />\n如果可以的話，最希望成世人周圍住，四海為家，今年住台灣，下年住瑞士，再下年住冰島。"},{"pid":"87e196ce15c11ecb61427be17fb7ee618d71179c","tid":1950514,"uid":194326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:23:13.000Z","msg":"講到自己咁sociable"},{"pid":"e88fea61de9b7d621c8bf39f420173c79afee3ea","tid":1950514,"uid":45268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:24:27.000Z","msg":"樓主應該好有錢"},{"pid":"906bb32f74f69870b6f0152902cfbd80f4ab575e","tid":1950514,"uid":214997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:25:42.000Z","msg":"驅除共黨之後會好好住"},{"pid":"8e405c2212a5ac5f02aed6a29d63977bd2201bf4","tid":1950514,"uid":353419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"906bb32f74f69870b6f0152902cfbd80f4ab575e","tid":1950514,"uid":214997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:25:42.000Z","msg":"驅除共黨之後會好好住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:26:46.000Z","msg":"係好住，但想廣闊視野"},{"pid":"738cd7307e02204d112070ea8bd19bc0ed92fb7b","tid":1950514,"uid":353419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e88fea61de9b7d621c8bf39f420173c79afee3ea","tid":1950514,"uid":45268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:24:27.000Z","msg":"樓主應該好有錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:27:46.000Z","msg":"其實讀書好似係想易移民"},{"pid":"9435e358d2dbe2301d97e18c4f71c099f53bc364","tid":1950514,"uid":336565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:30:28